Combine 1 cup water and brown rice in a medium microwave-safe bowl; cover. Microwave on HIGH 4 minutes. Microwave on MEDIUM 5 minutes. Fluff with a fork. Let cool to room temperature. Add carrot and next 4 ingredients; toss gently to combine. Combine vinegar and next 5 ingredients, stirring with a whisk. Add to rice mixture; toss gently to combine.